E_{ij}=-\frac{1}{\pi^{2}}\int_{0}^{1}dx\phi_{i}\left(x\right)\cdot\left(\nabla^{2}\phi_{j}\left(x\right)\right)+\frac{1}{2}m\omega^{2}\int_{0}^{1}dx\phi_{i}\left(x\right)\left(x-\frac{1}{2}\right)^{2}\phi_{j}\left(x\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset

which will change the energy eigenvalues.
 Defining 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha^{2}=\frac{m^{2}\omega^{2}}{2\hbar^{2}}$
\end_inset

, we have
