\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\Psi_{n_{1},n_{2}}^{\left(\pm,j\right)}\left(\overrightarrow{r}\right)=N_{n_{1},n_{2}}^{\left(\pm\right)}\left[\phi_{n_{1},n_{2}}^{\left(j\right)}\left(\overrightarrow{r}\right)\ket{\uparrow}+\chi_{n_{1},n_{2}}^{\left(\pm,j\right)}\left(\overrightarrow{r}\right)\ket{\downarrow}\right],\ \ \ \forall j=1,2
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{\uparrow}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{\downarrow}$
\end_inset

