\begin_layout Standard
The 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{6v}$
\end_inset

 group has 12 elements, and its character table is reproduced in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Character-table-ofc6-1"
